k memecoins dominated, affecting mid-tier projects.","id":"c7d94360-029e-43ae-b323-3a4abdd6c709","is_major":false,"source":"Cointelegraph","source_type":"news","summary":"During the third quarter, Bitcoin along with low-cap, high-risk memecoins showed significant performance in the crypto market. This trend resulted in venture capitalists paying less attention to mid-tier projects. This highlights the dominance and influence of these cryptocurrencies with Bitcoin showing a notable increase in value, while memecoins with low market capitalization and high-risk factors also experienced growth. As a result, investors have shifted their focus towards these higher-performing assets, potentially impacting the development and funding of mid-tier projects within the cryptocurrency space.","tickers":[],"time":"02:35:31","timestamp":"2024-10-17T02:35:31Z","url":"https://cointelegraph.com/news/crypto-vc-funding-drops-q3-projects-overlooked-galaxy-digital?utm_source=rss_feed&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rss_partner_inbound"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"crypto","date":"2024-10-17","headline":"Vitalik Buterin on Ethereum's future: 'The Surge' eyes 100,000+ TPS through sharding and rollups for scalability and decentralization.","id":"be579326-c33e-409d-af0b-6b9753410c3a","is_major":false,"source":"Blockchain News","source_type":"news","summary":"In a recent discussion with 'The Surge', Vitalik Buterin delved into Ethereum's upcoming advancements, particularly emphasizing scalability and decentralization. This includes implementing sharding and rollups to enhance performance, with the goal of achieving over 100,000 transactions per second (TPS). The discussion highlighted Ethereum's strategic vision for the future, aiming to address key challenges and improve the overall efficiency of the platform.","tickers":[],"time":"02:34:50","timestamp":"2024-10-17T02:34:50Z","url":"https://Blockchain.News/news/exploring-ethereum-future-the-surge-scalability"},{"beta_headline":null,"categ